<D>__{of course i will come.}
<C>__{mother}
<D>__{we didn't think you'd want to.}
<C>__{sharon}
<D>__{why not?}
<A>__{now her mother shows a trace of fear. she says gently...}
<C>__{mother}
<D>__{we don't want any trouble... on that day. please.}
<C>__{sharon}
<D>__{mom, i'm your daughter. i don't want any trouble ever. i will come to the ceremony. i won't come to argue, and i won't come in uniform.}
